    "Their system uses data collected from Swiss national television and synthetic ADs generated with DeepL, demonstrating improved translation quality through both automatic and human evaluations.",
    "However, while promising strides have been made in AD translation research, it remains underexplored and not yet fully integrated into AD production pipelines.",
    "More research is needed to refine these models and establish their role in practical applications, ensuring they meet the high standards required for AD production.",
    "As an inclusive product, ADs have greatly enhanced access to information for blind persons and persons with visual impairments.",
    "However, traditional AD production, which relies on human audio describers, is often both costly and time-consuming."
